#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn47.50"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.50:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.50:0.2"
msgid "5. Amatavagga "
msgstr "5. The Deathless "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.50:0.3"
msgid "50. Āsavasutta "
msgstr "50. Defilements "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.190, sc1
msgctxt "sn47.50:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave āsavā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three defilements. "

msgctxt "sn47.50:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "sn47.50:1.3"
msgid "Kāmāsavo, bhavāsavo, avijjāsavo—"
msgstr "The defilements of sensuality, desire to be reborn, and ignorance. "

msgctxt "sn47.50:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo āsavā. "
msgstr "These are the three defilements. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.50:1.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇannaṃ āsavānaṃ pahānāya cattāro satipaṭṭhānā bhāvetabbā. "
msgstr "The four kinds of mindfulness meditation should be developed to give up these three defilements. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn47.50:2.1"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn47.50:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ; "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

msgctxt "sn47.50:2.3"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe … "
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings … "

msgctxt "sn47.50:2.4"
msgid "citte … pe … "
msgstr "mind … "

msgctxt "sn47.50:2.5"
msgid "dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. "
msgstr "principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.50:2.6"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇannaṃ āsavānaṃ pahānāya ime cattāro satipaṭṭhānā bhāvetabbā”ti. "
msgstr "These four kinds of mindfulness meditation should be developed to give up these three defilements.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.50:2.7"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.50:2.8"
msgid "Amatavaggo pañcamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn47.50:3.1"
msgid "Amataṃ samudayo maggo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn47.50:3.2"
msgid "Sati kusalarāsi ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn47.50:3.3"
msgid "Pātimokkhaṃ duccaritaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn47.50:3.4"
msgid "Mittavedanā āsavena cāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
